stockindex <- function(n = 1000, p = .55) {
  ifelse(runif(n - 1) > 1 - p, 1 + .01, 1 - .01) |> 
    cumprod()
}

f <- .5
m <- 1000
s <- stockindex()

accumulate(
  .x = s,
  .f = ~ {
    keep = floor(.x * (1 - f))
    play = .x - keep
    earned = floor(keep + floor(play * .y))
    message("K:", round(keep), "p", round(play), "x", round(.y, 4), "e", round(earned))
    earned
    },
  .init = m
) |>
